### Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products

### Get product by id (exists)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/1

### Get product by id (does NOT exist — expect 404)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/999

### Get with string id (expect 404 — constraint blocks it)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/abc

### Create a product
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "price": 129.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/2

### Try deleting again (expect 404)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/2# For more info on HTTP files go to https://aka.ms/vs/httpfile
